Class AbstractStringConverter

  • java.lang.Object
    • ie.gmit.dip.AbstractStringConverter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:

    public abstract class AbstractStringConverter
extends java.lang.Object
implements AbstractConverter<java.lang.String,​java.lang.String>
    AbstractStringConverter is an abstract base class which implements the AbstractConverter interface. It is configured to take a String as input, and return a String as output. The specifics of the convert method are implemented by specialized concrete base types which inherit from this abstract class.
